            "id": 6430076,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 櫃買市場加權指數下跌-19點至376.08點，跌幅4.81%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間23日10:43，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌19點（或4.81%），暫報376.08點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+9.79%</li><li>近 1 月：+20.3%</li><li>近 3 月：+32.66%</li><li>近 6 月：+49.39%</li><li>今年以來：+43.02%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>被動元件概念領跌-6.78%。其中    希華(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2484:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2484\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2484-TW</a>)            下跌        10%            ;        加高(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8182:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8182\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8182-TW</a>)            下跌        9.99%            ;        台嘉碩(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3221:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3221\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3221-TW</a>)            下跌        9.92%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>SDN概念領跌-6.69%。其中    明泰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3380:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3380\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3380-TW</a>)            下跌        8.88%            ;        眾達-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>)            下跌        7.85%            ;        安瑞-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3664:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3664\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3664-TW</a>)            下跌        7.63%    。</p></section></main>",
